Create ECS component for viewport windowing.

## Component Design

```typescript
const VirtualViewport = {
  // Viewport window
  firstVisibleLine: Uint32Array,   // First line index in view
  visibleLineCount: Uint32Array,   // Number of lines in viewport

  // Content info
  totalLineCount: Uint32Array,     // Total lines in data

  // Overscan (render extra lines for smooth scroll)
  overscanBefore: Uint8Array,      // Extra lines above viewport
  overscanAfter: Uint8Array,       // Extra lines below viewport

  // Performance hints
  estimatedLineHeight: Uint8Array, // For variable height estimation
  isVariableHeight: Uint8Array,    // 0=fixed, 1=variable
};
```

